{
  "stem": "12684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hamburg had a touch of communism in them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since it's a big harbor, their horizon is completely different as those who were inland or never saw other people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I believe it was not as hard for the people in Hamburg, in comparison as to those in Berlin and Wiesbaden, Baden-Baden, and all these other little cities.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they had still some trades, the Germans, with Holland, and with Sweden and Denmark.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, of course, the overseas and stopped completely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That's all what I know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because many ships didn't come anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were forbidden, well, allowed or forbidden or whatever, because the Germans didn't have the money to pay for the merchandise.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they wanted it but they didn't have it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Personally, I hated it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hated the idea that it was so dangerous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hated the idea that everything was a risk until my mother explained to me is everybody and everyday is a risk in life.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is just another risk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She's very down to earth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they had the bombardments in Hamburg, we all had to go into the basement for safety.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was not allowed to go to their basement, so they had to find an extra little basement for myself and the maid we had.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother was in the hospital at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as it turned out, my little cellar was much more secure as the other one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they realized what a ridiculous thing it was, so they wanted me to come back again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, no, no, it's more secure here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I stay here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You want to come here, come here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they started it in '39 sometime or '40.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think the English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some intestinal thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
